    "name": "Ved : Journey Beyond the Cube",
    "steam_appid": 3246430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/07a1c44328fa6c30bdfb70a453c7944d.webp?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/507f6cac9f7fdf7d83bc855e65eb41a0.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/507f6cac9f7fdf7d83bc855e65eb41a0.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/507f6cac9f7fdf7d83bc855e65eb41a0.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ved’s life changes the moment he touches the ancient cube.<br>A hidden force awakens, pulling his soul inside and trapping him in a new form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, as a cube, he must uncover why he was chosen, explore his past, and find a way to break the curse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/e9bc9c5a776ca476a773bc092afd7951.webp?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/b7006af64db6bedec16393c021a80520.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/b7006af64db6bedec16393c021a80520.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/b7006af64db6bedec16393c021a80520.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each puzzle uses what a cube can do.<br>Push blocks, activate switches, and control magical energy to solve ancient mechanisms<br>From pushing blocks to redirecting energy, every puzzle is built around your cube form and elemental powers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/d0f69bb27ba0ad10e782cb7f26c8268d.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/d0f69bb27ba0ad10e782cb7f26c8268d.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/d0f69bb27ba0ad10e782cb7f26c8268d.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your cube’s power to destroy obstacles and open new routes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/44470808308211a23aaecce4c21404d8.webp?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/3c3bb7075953abfb81227331c9199bf1.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/3c3bb7075953abfb81227331c9199bf1.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/3c3bb7075953abfb81227331c9199bf1.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re not just solving puzzles — you’re uncovering Ved’s story.<br>You follow his past, his curse, and how he became a cube.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/ac4f07891c3a131cd1180ae25a84db6b.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/07c04a9403f0edb1fc1d65fc014f45c4.webp?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/4b71f8fcfe0fd3e48ed87d54d0ff9e6d.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/4b71f8fcfe0fd3e48ed87d54d0ff9e6d.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/4b71f8fcfe0fd3e48ed87d54d0ff9e6d.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIRE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire represents <strong>energy, transformation, and the power to purify</strong>.<br>It is the element of change, warmth, and turning darkness into light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Fire power, Ved can hold and control flames within his cube.<br>This lets him carry fire safely, ignite ancient mechanisms, and convert negative energy into positive energy to clear the path ahead </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UPCOMING CHAPTERS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/4c208ed4f7044ea7cdc4791dab9b7070.webp?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/5a6f8db138721d31cea1ffa752536df0.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/5a6f8db138721d31cea1ffa752536df0.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/5a6f8db138721d31cea1ffa752536df0.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARTH</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earth represents <strong>structure, shape, and the strength to support life</strong>.<br>It is the element of stability and solid form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Earth power, Ved can attach nearby cubes to himself.<br>This lets him grow, extend, and create stable shapes to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/b9cb12824f1156ba7bde2b3f87248935.webp?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/e5db87ed264aec7c9691f301b5059af4.poster.avif?t=1766984285\" width=1080 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/e5db87ed264aec7c9691f301b5059af4.webm?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246430/extras/e5db87ed264aec7c9691f301b5059af4.mp4?t=1766984285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AIR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Air represents <strong>movement, lightness, and the freedom to rise</strong>.<br>It is the element of speed, motion, and breath that carries life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Air power, Ved can lift himself using controlled wind currents.<br>This lets him rise above platforms, glide across gaps, and move faster without rolling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
